message: Trying to make the page more balanced and erase deliberate falsifications
A user with the handle Mkdw has vandalized Solomon's Wikipedia page.

WIKIPEDIA PLEASE HELP! Someone with a hostile agenda keeps adding false and excessively negative material to this entry, and removing any positive information, such as the "awards and honors" section.
Deleted excessively negative material written by an anonymous "hater."

I am sorry to report that a someone added incorrect statements of a hostile and even libelous nature to this page this month. I have deleted the untruths and hope this page can now stand as is, without further interference from "haters."

Deleted "liberal" from one-sentence introductory synopsis. This sort of ideological red-flagging is suspicious; it's not routinely done on Wikipedia, so why here, in the case of a female, Jewish New Yorker? Let her ideas speak for themselves.
